title: [Guardian Keep, Grassy Sward]
description: Various tents have been strategically placed near the bubbling fresh water fountain that provides for the needs of the merchants in this grassy area.  The occasional passerby wanders up to the fountain and scoops out a drink before ambling off to complete other errands.

Various tents have been strategically placed near the bubbling fresh water fountain that provides for the needs of the merchants in this grassy area.  The bubbling fountain attracts the occasional nighttime passerby who wanders up to the fountain and quenches his or her thirst before ambling off to complete other errands.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
